- [Red] Long red cable from ESP’s Vin (next to USB) to 5V of the (red) LED board
- [Red] ESP’s 3V3 to VIN of the purple board
- [Black] ESP’s GND to the purple and LED board’s GND
- [Orange] ESP’s D4 pin to DI of the LED board
- [Green or white] ESP’s D2 to purple board’s SDA
- [Yellow] ESP’s D1 to purple board’s SCL
